---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Airbourne Lens">
  <section class="about-page">
    <div class="about-intro">
      <h1 class="about-title">About Airbourne Lens</h1>
      <p class="about-tagline">
        Capturing the world from unique perspectives&nbsp;&mdash; in the air and on the ground.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-body">
      <p>
        I&rsquo;m a drone enthusiast filming in 4K, using the DJI Neo, DJI Mini&nbsp;4&nbsp;Pro,
        DJI Air&nbsp;3S (with RC2 controller), and the DJI Osmo Pocket&nbsp;3 for smooth
        cinematic ground shots.
      </p>

      <p>
        From the dramatic coastlines and historic landmarks of the UK to the crystal-clear
        waters of the Maldives and Mauritius, the lush green jungles of Costa Rica and Mexico,
        and the sunlit shores of Cyprus&nbsp;&mdash; my videos blend aerial footage and ground views
        to bring each location to life.
      </p>

      <h2 class="about-subheading">Expect</h2>
      <ul class="about-list">
        <li>Breathtaking drone videography and cinematic travel films</li>
        <li>Footage of nature, heritage sites, beaches, mountains, impressive structures and cities</li>
        <li>Global locations filmed with DJI drones and professional gimbal cameras</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="about-note">
        No paid promotions&nbsp;&mdash; just a passion for drone flying, filmmaking,
        and exploring the world.
      </p>

      <a
        class="subscribe-link"
        href="https://youtube.com/@AirbourneLens"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        <svg class="about-yt-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z" />
        </svg>
        Subscribe on YouTube
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    max-width: 40rem;
  }

  .about-intro {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #e8e4dd;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-tagline {
    color: #d4a84b;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-body p {
    color: #a09ba0;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .about-subheading {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #e8e4dd;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-list li {
    color: #a09ba0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.55rem;
    width: 0.4rem;
    height: 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background-color: #d4a84b;
  }

  .about-note {
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .subscribe-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    align-self: flex-start;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: #d4a84b;
    color: #16161a;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.15s;
  }

  .subscribe-link:hover {
    background-color: #c49a3f;
  }

  .about-yt-icon {
    width: 1.15rem;
    height: 1.15rem;
  }
</style>
